{"tid":1183583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"比間垃圾公司昆鳩錢","createTime":"2019-06-03T04:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T00:29:50.000Z","uid":224521,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a8b36c8ebf8f35c158004c7e859f1bd9fb40179f","tid":1183583,"uid":224521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:31:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/92z7PZi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F92z7PZi.jpg&h=69fb9672&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說小弟不久之前買左一架航拍機。<br />\n寄到嚟發現4個摩打入面有一個function 唔到。一飛就失平衡墜機。咁我就同番個代理講啦。<br />\n<br />\n我要求佢換過架比我，畢竟佢講過7日內有壞包換。<br />\n<br />\n然後佢同我講架機花左唔換得？！<br />\n咁架機本來就係壞嘅。正因為佢壞左，咁飛嘅時候咪失平衡，最後整花左。<br />\n<br />\n而家點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7fd06317a78a1d4106ada31cdff424243deb95","tid":1183583,"uid":222039,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:34:49.000Z","msg":"聽日十二點前比到一個你滿意既答覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nChing你串左少少"},{"pid":"67af23ef8836ab831b54fff99d9111d4245bf049","tid":1183583,"uid":30708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:35:22.000Z","msg":"post張無cover嘅cap圖先"},{"pid":"a3501f6b1e6c3164147fb996ac4e847859387929","tid":1183583,"uid":224521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7f7fd06317a78a1d4106ada31cdff424243deb95","tid":1183583,"uid":222039,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:34:49.000Z","msg":"聽日十二點前比到一個你滿意既答覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nChing你串左少少"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:36:18.000Z","msg":"因為間公司已經拖左我成個禮拜<br />\n我冇辦法先咁講"},{"pid":"f51e5dd9d6883e059a63fe771653aee7e3c6de0b","tid":1183583,"uid":63950,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:37:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebaf6e0d88626a6c138a79b2472